            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>pro salute et <lb n="3"/>incolumitate <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>eri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Tib</abbr><ex>erini</ex></expan> Marciani <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Iunior</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Marcianus <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>dupl</abbr><ex>arius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> X <expan><abbr>gem</abbr><ex>inae</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>Antoninian<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>adiut</abbr><ex>or</ex></expan> p<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">raef(ecti)</supplied> <lb n="10"/><supplied reason="lost">et <expan><abbr>Gr</abbr><ex>a</ex>ecinia</expan> <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="11"/><supplied reason="lost">Priscilla</supplied> <lb n="12"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>parent</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olverunt</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Der untere Teil mit dem Ende der Z. 9 u. den Z. 10-12 war bei der Auffindung noch vorhanden. Z. 4: Auflösung Tib(erini) nach Alföldy. Z. 9: überliefert ist PRAETER. (B): CIL 03, 04030: Z. 9: adiu[t. Datierung: wegen des Legionsbeinamens Antoniniana zur Zeit des Caracalla oder Elagabal.</p>
            </div>
